name: Other Miscellaneous Projects
description:
Game #1: Super Smash Bros. Ultimate Jeopardy! - Test your knowledge and trivia of Super Smash Bros. Ultimate! Can you answer all of the questions correctly?

Game #2: Python Arcade - Have some fun with some programs made in Python, such as "Rock, Paper, Scissors" and "War", and ask fate defining questions to the Magic 8 Ball!
